item.title: 8 point at Math
item.description: ORIGINAL LINK Guessing the selections on the paper, there was only one idea that I wanted to destroy the fucking campus. With the time going, it was only anxious spirits that ran around my mind. Sleepy and a little mad, I fell asleep while guessing and writing the shit “A B C D”, and suddenly woke up again and again. Surely, I admit that I got trapped in the absent-minded stats, which made me buried in the temporary dreams.
